    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3110668553" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12315184517493105418">A hugely popular memoir of a man I admired far more before I actually read it. A pretty straightforward run down of his life and career, it suffers from dated attitudes and a probable skating over of some very bad behaviour. Strangely it retains a gruesome, voyeuristic interest. How many names can one man drop? I lost count...</span>

          </span>
        </div>


